1. Project Overview 1

CAI is Computer Aided Instructor which monitors Colaberry Database 24/7 to look for ways to help, alert and improve performance by sending out emails.  The CAI Email Dashboard in Power BI provides statistics of emails getting sent out.


Below are some of the KPIs created using DAX measures:

  • Total Emails Sent
  •  Email Open Rate
  •  Email Click Rate
  •  Total Email Opens
  •  Average Emails per day


    • The above measures were sliced and diced using the following dimensions:

  • Time
  • Severity
  • Email Groups
  • Campaigns


    • Different visualizations were used to present the above information to create the final dashboard shown below.


    Dashboard Overview

    The Overview tab shows the Total emails sent, Email Opens and Email Clicks over time, Emails sent to different Groups, % of Emails by Severity and Top and Bottom 10 Campaigns. Highs level KPIs are shown on the left. Different time periods can be selected on the time slicer to show information accordingly. Additionally, we can select specific Email groups and Severity in the hidden slicer. A navigation bar is provided on the top to navigate to different report pages.




    Open Rate

    On this tab, the heat map displays email open rate by different group and severity. A Matrix to show all the details of all the Email Groups, Campaigns, Severity, Total Emails Sent, Total Opens, Email Open Rate and Email Click Rate.


    Top Recipients

    On this tab, the top 10 email recipients in the system are displayed. Different Email groups or severity can be selected in the slicers to display the top 10 recipients accordingly. We can select a specific individual and drill through to Person detail page.



    Campaign Trends

    This tab shows the trend of email campaigns by group over time. Selecting a specific group will show the trend of corresponding email campaigns accordingly. Also the hidden slicer on this page can help slice the data by a specific time period and severity.



    Person Detail

    This tab shows the Email journey of a person over time. It gives a general idea about what kind of emails were sent out to him/her from the start of their journey with Colaberry to end. We can search for a certain person in the Name slicer or drill through from the Top 10 Recipient page to see the emails specific to that person.
